snippet.title: Fly O'Clock by Digital Melody Games
snippet.description:
Fly O’Clock from creators of Timberman and Surfingers is here!

Second hand is dangerous, isn’t it? Jump, jump, jump on the clock face to survive. Beat the high-score, unlock all the charming insects, watches and hats!

- one-touch controls
- brand new jumpy gameplay
- 15+ characters to unlock
- 5+ watches to jump on
- 15+ hats to try on
